Some useful links to wrap one's head around criteria API:
https://developer.ibm.com/articles/j-typesafejpa/
https://docs.oracle.com/javaee/6/tutorial/doc/gjitv.html

Properties to run this application:
-Djavax.persistence.jdbc.driver=com.mysql.cj.jdbc.Driver
-Djavax.persistence.jdbc.url="jdbc:mysql://${host}:${port}/${db-name}"
-Dhibernate.connection.username=${username}
-Dhibernate.connection.password=${password}
-Dhibernate.show_sql=true
-Dhibernate.format_sql=true
